---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base title="Gist — Turn your app idea into a build-ready spec">
  <header class="site-header">
    <div class="container">
      <a href="/" class="logo" aria-label="Gist home">Gist</a>
    </div>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="hero">
      <div class="container">
        <h1 class="hero-title">
          Describe your idea.<br />
          <span class="hero-accent">Get a spec AI can build from.</span>
        </h1>
        <p class="hero-subtitle">
          Answer a few questions about your app — what it does, who it's for, where the data lives.
          Gist turns your answers into a deployment-ready specification that Claude, Cursor, or Codex
          can implement without the back-and-forth.
        </p>
        <div class="hero-actions">
          <a href="/create" class="btn btn-primary">Create your spec</a>
          <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn btn-ghost">See how it works</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section id="how-it-works" class="steps">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Three steps to a build-ready spec</h2>
        <ol class="step-list">
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">1</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Describe your idea</h3>
              <p>Title, one-line description, and what your users see first. No jargon required.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">2</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Answer a few questions</h3>
              <p>We ask about data, hosting, and design. Every option is laid out with trade-offs visible — pick what fits, skip what doesn't matter.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
          <li class="step">
            <span class="step-number">3</span>
            <div class="step-content">
              <h3>Download your spec</h3>
              <p>A markdown file with architecture decisions, security guidance, implementation order, and a suggested prompt for your AI assistant.</p>
            </div>
          </li>
        </ol>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="spec-preview-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">What you get</h2>
        <p class="section-subtitle">A real spec — not a template. Tailored to your answers, right-sized to your app's complexity.</p>
        <div class="spec-preview">
          <div class="spec-preview-header">
            <span class="spec-preview-dot"></span>
            <span class="spec-preview-dot"></span>
            <span class="spec-preview-dot"></span>
            <span class="spec-preview-filename">weather-now-gist-spec-v1.0.md</span>
          </div>
          <pre class="spec-preview-body"><code># Weather Now — Gist Specification

## Meta
- Gist version: 1.0
- Complexity tier: minimal

## Summary
> A clutter-free personal weather app. Fetches weather
> from Open-Meteo (free, no key) directly from the
> browser. Plain HTML/CSS/JS — no framework, no build
> step, no server. Deploy static files to Cloudflare Pages.

## Architecture
- Host: Cloudflare Pages (free tier)
- Framework: None — plain HTML/CSS/JS
- Proxy: None (API is free, no key needed)

## Implementation Order
1. Scaffold: index.html, style.css, app.js, favicon
2. HTML shell with loading/error/success states
3. Styles: cool palette, dark mode, responsive
4. Connect: Open-Meteo API + Nominatim geocoding
5. Web standards: og:image, CSP, meta tags
6. Deploy: push to Cloudflare Pages

## Suggested Prompt
"Build step by step, starting with mock data..."</code></pre>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="value-props">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="section-title">Why a spec matters</h2>
        <div class="value-grid">
          <article class="value-card">
            <h3>Right-sized architecture</h3>
            <p>A simple app gets 4 static files. A complex one gets Workers, KV, and cron. Your spec matches your actual needs.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <h3>Security from the start</h3>
            <p>API keys never touch your frontend. Trust boundaries are explicit. The pre-ship checklist catches what you'd miss.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <h3>Less back-and-forth</h3>
            <p>Without a spec, Claude asks a dozen clarifying questions. With one, it can start building immediately.</p>
          </article>
          <article class="value-card">
            <h3>Free tier aware</h3>
            <p>Every recommendation fits within free tier limits. Budget math is included — no surprise charges.</p>
          </article>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <section class="cta-section">
      <div class="container">
        <h2 class="cta-title">Ready to build something?</h2>
        <p class="cta-subtitle">Five minutes of questions. A spec you can hand to any AI coding assistant.</p>
        <a href="/create" class="btn btn-primary btn-lg">Create your spec</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>

  <footer class="site-footer">
    <div class="container">
      <p>Built with Gist. Open source on <a href="https://github.com/1mb-dev/gistapp" class="footer-link">GitHub</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </footer>
</Base>

<style>
  /* header */
  .site-header {
    padding: var(--space-5) 0;
  }

  .logo {
    font-size: var(--text-xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    color: var(--color-text);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  /* hero */
  .hero {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0 var(--space-12);
    text-align: center;
  }

  .hero-title {
    font-size: var(--text-3xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    line-height: var(--leading-tight);
    letter-spacing: -0.03em;
    color: var(--color-text);
    max-width: 600px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .hero-accent {
    color: var(--color-accent);
  }

  .hero-subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-6);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    max-width: 540px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .hero-actions {
    margin-top: var(--space-8);
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    justify-content: center;
    flex-wrap: wrap;
  }

  /* buttons */
  .btn {
    display: inline-flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-6);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-medium);
    cursor: pointer;
    border: none;
    transition: background var(--duration-fast) var(--easing),
                color var(--duration-fast) var(--easing),
                box-shadow var(--duration-fast) var(--easing);
    min-height: 44px;
    text-decoration: none;
  }

  .btn-primary {
    background: var(--color-accent);
    color: var(--color-accent-text);
  }

  .btn-primary:hover {
    background: var(--color-accent-hover);
  }

  .btn-ghost {
    background: transparent;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
  }

  .btn-ghost:hover {
    background: var(--color-bg-overlay);
    color: var(--color-text);
    border-color: var(--color-border);
  }

  .btn-lg {
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-8);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
  }

  /* steps */
  .steps {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
  }

  .section-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
    text-align: center;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
  }

  .section-subtitle {
    text-align: center;
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    font-size: var(--text-lg);
    margin-top: calc(-1 * var(--space-6));
    margin-bottom: var(--space-10);
    max-width: 520px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .step-list {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-6);
    max-width: 480px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .step {
    display: flex;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    align-items: flex-start;
  }

  .step-number {
    flex-shrink: 0;
    width: 36px;
    height: 36px;
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: var(--color-accent-subtle);
    color: var(--color-accent);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
  }

  .step-content h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-1);
  }

  .step-content p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* spec preview */
  .spec-preview-section {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0 var(--space-16);
  }

  .spec-preview {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border);
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    overflow: hidden;
    box-shadow: var(--shadow-lg);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .spec-preview-header {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-2);
    padding: var(--space-3) var(--space-4);
    background: var(--color-bg-sunken);
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
  }

  .spec-preview-dot {
    width: 10px;
    height: 10px;
    border-radius: var(--radius-full);
    background: var(--color-border);
  }

  .spec-preview-filename {
    margin-left: var(--space-2);
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .spec-preview-body {
    padding: var(--space-5);
    overflow-x: auto;
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-xs);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: none;
    margin: 0;
  }

  .spec-preview-body code {
    background: none;
    padding: 0;
    font-size: inherit;
  }

  /* value props */
  .value-props {
    padding: var(--space-12) 0;
    background: var(--color-bg-sunken);
  }

  .value-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    gap: var(--space-5);
    max-width: 560px;
    margin-inline: auto;
  }

  .value-card {
    background: var(--color-bg-raised);
    border: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    padding: var(--space-6);
  }

  .value-card h3 {
    font-size: var(--text-base);
    font-weight: var(--weight-semibold);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-2);
  }

  .value-card p {
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    line-height: var(--leading-relaxed);
  }

  /* CTA */
  .cta-section {
    padding: var(--space-16) 0;
    text-align: center;
  }

  .cta-title {
    font-size: var(--text-2xl);
    font-weight: var(--weight-bold);
    letter-spacing: -0.02em;
  }

  .cta-subtitle {
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-8);
  }

  /* footer */
  .site-footer {
    padding: var(--space-8) 0;
    border-top: 1px solid var(--color-border-subtle);
    text-align: center;
    font-size: var(--text-sm);
    color: var(--color-text-muted);
  }

  .footer-link {
    color: var(--color-text-secondary);
    text-decoration: underline;
    text-underline-offset: 2px;
  }

  .footer-link:hover {
    color: var(--color-text);
  }

  /* responsive */
  @media (min-width: 640px) {
    .hero-title {
      font-size: var(--text-4xl);
    }

    .value-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr 1fr;
      max-width: 100%;
    }
  }
</style>
